{
  "stem": "6258.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "00 and 2:00, we came for-- for soup back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then back to work and about 6 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "5:00, 6:00.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, street cleaning.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People were working in the washers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People were working with tailor shop, with, well, like--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not-- not doing these things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were just doing the menial work, scrubbing the floor, cleaning the windows, working on the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, these kind of things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, sometimes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I even did also this for quite a few months, doing files for exchange part for the airplanes in the magazine.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only difference was like this that we were being painted here--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and here, everything--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--clothes, dresses.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And here, big number.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes,that's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--work was the same.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, as long we were under-- under-- with that Air Force, it was different.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It depends.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe someone was really terrible, well, depending on the human character.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No. 1943, there was the end of this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they said that-- in-- in-- about six months earlier, we were taken so that we belonged to Fliegerhorst.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they closed--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the camp and took us to Plaszow, all of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we were still there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But-- but then we were still at Fliegerhorst when Fliegerhorst was taken over administratively--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--by this.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were still in Fliegerhorst.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in December, they closed the-- the camp and took us all to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was there maybe for about a month, when I was taken to another camp, also of the Air Force.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, something like this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Plaszow scared me to death.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had absolutely no idea about.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
